Tuambie kilichotokea baadaye.

0:08:06.460,0:08:09.840
Ninafuraha sana na nina fahari kuwa hapa.

0:08:09.840,0:08:11.420
Halleluya!

0:08:11.420,0:08:15.360
Ushahidi wa Kristo Yesu ni mabadiliko katika maisha.

