Kabla, nilikuwa na uhusiano na wanawake na sikuwaona wanaume kama wanaume - niliwaona wanawake kama wanaume.

0:08:41.980,0:08:46.480
Lakini sasa, nikiwaona wanawake, nawaona kama wanawake na wanaume kama wanaume.

0:08:46.480,0:08:48.880
Ninamshukuru Mungu kwa hilo.

0:08:48.880,0:08:56.180
Jana, kaka  yangu alinipigia na kuniuliza deni la ya kodi ya tangu nisafiri kuja Nigeria

0:08:56.180,0:09:00.220
na ni kiasi gani nilichokuwa nadaiwa kama kodi ya nyumba yangu - nilishangaa.

0:09:00.220,0:09:02.720
Hii haijawahi kutokea!

0:09:02.720,0:09:07.920
Hakuna mtu aliyewaihi kupiga simu na  kuniuliza kuhusu kulipa madeni yangu,  nilifurahi!

0:09:07.920,0:09:10.300
Aliahidi kwamba angenilipia kodi.

0:09:10.300,0:09:15.600
Halleluya! Hebu tupige makofi kwa ajili ya Yesu!

0:09:15.600,0:09:20.680
Umesikiliza kuhusu ushuhuda kutoka kwa dada yetu kuhusu kubadilisha maisha yake

0:09:20.680,0:09:24.400
