0:10:43.460,0:10:47.060
ambao wamekuja kwa SCOAN.

0:10:47.060,0:10:52.220
Wakati Nabii TB Joshua akiendelea kuwaombea, anakutana na mwanamke huyu,

0:10:52.220,0:10:55.140
ambaye mara moja mapepo yanaanza kujidhihirisha.

